    "summary": "The user asks for a geopolitical assessment of the 2011 Libya intervention, specifically questioning if it was a success or a mess. The assistant consistently characterizes the intervention as a strategic failure and a \"blunder,\" dismissing the humanitarian argument as \"naive and dangerous\" in favor of a realpolitik focus on state stability.",
